reviewText: Insane! Insane! So FREAKING INSANE!! Man, Round 2 of Baki the Grappler is CRAZY! I thought Round 1 was crazy but obviously Round takes it. I just assume the series is just going to get crazier and crazier as it goes along, so Round 2 may not be the craziest out of all the volumes. I have to make sure by obtaining all of the volumes. I can say so much but the word Insane is the best way to describe it. If your not serious and you laugh and things that were ment to be serious and you like anime watch this. also if you enjoyed the first volume I would assume you would have the whole series if not get this!
